text:
[Verse]
Stars in the sky
Shining so bright
Heartbeat tonight
Lost in the light

[Verse 2]
Feet on the ground
Spin me around
Feel the sound
In this town

[Chorus]
Moonlit dance
Take a chance
In romance
Just a glance

[Verse 3]
Whispers so clear
In my ear
You are here
Hold me near

[Bridge]
Sky so high
You and I
Never shy
Touch the sky

[Chorus]
Moonlit dance
Take a chance
In romance
Just a glance
title: Moonlit Dance
